Event description: Enjoy a beautiful ride to Eze village from Nice city by E Bike. Those are amazing bikes with electrical assistance. You just feel the freedom of a great ride, without the pain when going uphill !&nbsp; 
<br>You will discover breathtaking views on your way along the Seaside to the Medieval village of Eze. Don't worry, picture times are planned on the schedule!&nbsp; 
<br>You will visit as well the Perfume factory Fragonard and have a free guided visit.&nbsp; 
<br> 
<br>This Tour is provided with a local professionnal guide who will tell you anecdots and tips for your stay in Nice. The groups are kept small to improve contact with the guide and links between the travellers. 
<br> 
<br>The tour lasts 4H in order to let you plenty of time to appreciate both the ride and the stop in Eze.<p>Enjoy a beautiful ride to Eze village from Nice city by E Bike. Those are amazing bikes with electrical assistance. You just feel the freedom of a great ride, without the pain when going uphill !&nbsp; 
<br>You will discover breathtaking views on your way along the Seaside to the Medieval village of Eze. Don't worry, picture times are planned on the schedule!&nbsp; 
<br>You will visit as well the Perfume factory Fragonard and have a free guided visit.&nbsp; 
<br> 
<br>This Tour is provided with a local professionnal guide who will tell you anecdots and tips for your stay in Nice. The groups are kept small to improve contact with the guide and links between the travellers. 
<br> 
<br>The tour lasts 4H in order to let you plenty of time to appreciate both the ride and the stop in Eze.<p>Starting from the Port of Nice, you will ride on low Corniche road to Villefranche s/Mer and start going uphill to Eze. Don't worry, you will reach 400m high without even beginning to sweat! Ok, except if it's during summer time, in this case I won't lie it's going to be hot. But that won't be because of the riding.&nbsp;&nbsp; 
<br>Along the way, you will have the opportunity to understand why the Cote d'Azur is one of the most beautiful area in France. Breathtaking views, blue sky, azur sea, forests, cliffs, ... Don't expect any less than that. 
<br> Then, Eze village will offer you a totally different atmosphere. Medieval environment, lots of local art shops, souvenir shops, small streets, old stone houses, ...&nbsp;
<br>The perfume factory and its visit will be another activity for you. The visit is free and a guide from Fragonard will tell you everything you need to know about perfume making. Very interesting ! You will obviously have the possibility to buy some souvenir from Fragonard. Amazing smell guaranteed.&nbsp;
<br>Given that the tour takes place over lunch time (10am to 2pm), your guide will show you a nice bakery to buy your picnic. Don't forget to bring some money for your lunch. Many places are great to stop and sit for lunch. Trust your guide!&nbsp;
<br>Also, a visit of the Flower Garden is on the schedule if you are willing to go. Plan to pay 6€ for the entrance ticket. It's worth it !&nbsp;
<br>
<br>Eventually, all the riders will follow the guide towards Nice. Tremendous views are all over the place also on the way back !&nbsp;
<br>
<br>Departure time : 10 am.&nbsp;
<br>Bring appropriate clothes for a nice ride under the sun. Don't forget your hat, suncream and sneakers.
<br>We will provide you with a mineral bottle of water.</p>

